sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Chat UI
    participant API as Chat API
    participant DB as Chat DB
    participant Rasa as Rasa Server
    participant NLU as Rasa NLU
    participant Core as Rasa Core
    participant Action as Action Server

    U->>FE: Nhap question
    FE->>API: POST /chat {conversationId, message}
    API->>DB: Luu user message
    API->>Rasa: POST /webhooks/rest/webhook
    Rasa->>NLU: Parse message
    NLU-->>Rasa: Intent, entities, confidence
    Rasa->>Core: Lay tracker va predict next action
    alt Can custom action
        Core->>Action: Run action voi slots/context
        Action-->>Core: Events va response
    else Response tinh trong domain
        Core-->>Rasa: Template response
    end
    Rasa-->>API: Bot response
    API->>DB: Luu bot message va metadata
    API-->>FE: Response JSON
    FE-->>U: Hien thi cau tra loi
